## Third-party model notice

This project uses Tencent's Hunyuan3D 2.1 model for image-to-3D generation.
The model is governed by the Tencent Hunyuan3D Community License
(https://huggingface.co/tencent/Hunyuan3D-2), which permits research and
commercial use subject to its terms. Distribution of this software does NOT
include the model weights — they are downloaded at build time from HuggingFace
under that license.
